X
([-1,2])
Y=|X|
f
|X|
 Ef(|X|) = \frac 13 \int_{-1}^2 f(|x|) dx =\frac 13 \int_{-1}^0 f(-x) dx + \frac 13 \int_0^2 f(x) dx \\ = \frac 13 \int_0^1 f(y) dy + \frac 13 \int_0^2 f(x) dx \\ = \int_0^1 g(x)f(x) dx  
 g(x) = \begin{cases}  \frac 23,  & 0\le x< 1\\ \frac 13,  & 1\le x\le 2 \end{cases} 
0\le x\le1
x<0
1<x\le2
x>2
P(Y\le x)=P(-x\le X\le x)=\frac{2x}{3}
